*[[河北省|河北省]][[张家口市|张家口市]]主城区北部的[[大境门|大境门]]<ref>[http://www.he.xinhuanet.com/zfwq/2009-10/28/content_18076643.htm 大境门长城文化旅游区建设项目] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110821191749/http://www.he.xinhuanet.com/zfwq/2009-10/28/content_18076643.htm |date=2011-08-21 }}</ref>；
